  "2187730": {
    "name": "IHAS",
    "steam_appid": 2187730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由乌克兰独立开发商精心制作：</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/8f930241f2327c655e38345bc7e2e20c.avif?t=1732201104\" width=616 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在这个科幻动作解谜第一人称射击游戏中，你将于一艘巨大的宇宙飞船中醒来。你失去了对过去的记忆，有个熟悉的声音声称是你的朋友，指引你一路前行。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索飞船</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在飞船上遍布敌对机器人的情况下，你必须穿过这艘飞船，找到逃生之路。随着你穿越能量门和变幻莫测的过道，你的心中一直有一阵预感挥之不去，告诉你表象之下潜藏的秘密就在不远处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.poster.avif?t=1732201104\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.webm?t=1732201104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加强与进化机械身体</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你的任务就此展开：当你在飞船中展开冒险、征服所面临的挑战，以及寻找通往自由的道路时，你会发现自己需要利用机器增强技术所蕴含的潜力。找到升级芯片并了解如何使用它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.poster.avif?t=1732201104\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.webm?t=1732201104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>改装武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随着探索的深入，你会发现敌人越来越强大。为武器装备不同改装件，从而完全释放其潜能。从强大的激光束到笨重的霰弹枪，根据自己的战斗风格自定义武器吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.poster.avif?t=1732201104\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.webm?t=1732201104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关卡编辑器  (BETA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在结束游戏后依旧意犹未尽？别担心——在社区的支持下，你可以通过Steam创意工坊创建并分享自己的关卡，畅享更多游戏激情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.poster.avif?t=1732201104\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.webm?t=1732201104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 引人入胜的科幻冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 第一人称射击动作战斗、解谜与头目战，畅享数小时游戏快感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 探索IHAS宇宙飞船的惊人景致</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 使用无缝菜单导航，沉浸感体验不打折扣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 升级武器与机械身体，轻松拿捏未来的挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - (BETA) 通过关卡编辑器与社区建立联系，每天可创建、分享并畅玩全新关卡！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语, 俄语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
